name: TANGLED
description:
(4/5) Social Norms and Misjudgments

Smothering her eyes with gauze, she hides away from her fears, for nothing in the world is truly perfect. To common belief, I can't see them, are the evils of the world really there? 

Model: Luisa I. Short  

This mint is created to help spread awareness and make meaningful impacts on those who need it within the community. This is a conceptual series related to the stereotypes and social norms we see in our daily lives.
